queryPatterns.pattern: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT STRING.STRING.STRING FROM STRING.STRING WHERE N=N OFFSET $?) AS STRING

SELECT STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING FROM STRING.STRING WHERE N=N ORDER BY STRING.STRING.STRING ASC LIMIT $? OFFSET $?

SELECT STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING FROM STRING.STRING WHERE STRING.STRING.STRING > $? ORDER BY STRING.STRING.STRING ASC LIMIT $? OFFSET $?

SELECT STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING, STRING.STRING.STRING FROM STRING.STRING WHERE STRING.STRING.STRING < $? OFFSET $?
